            <summary>Manuscript is used for contemplation and study and is a Hindu philosophical treatise whose title is translated as Honey of Advaita; is also a summary and synopsis of the fundamentals of the Advaita Vedānta school of philosophy; the work also contains an extensive commentary by Svayamprakāśa titled Dhyānadīpa.</summary>
